org.opcfoundation.ua.common

Class NamespaceTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opcfoundation.ua.common.UriTable
      • org.opcfoundation.ua.common.NamespaceTable

  • public class NamespaceTable
extends UriTable
    The table of name space URIs for a server. The table enables mapping between name space indexes and URIs. Use add to add entries to the table. Use getIndex to find the index of an URI or getUri to find the Uri of an index.
